Title: An Act Changing the Name of Sibalom Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sibalom, Province of Antique, to Delegate Ramon Maza, Sr. Memorial Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 77
An Act Changing the Name of Sibalom Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sibalom, Province of Antique, to Delegate Ramon Maza, Sr. Memorial Hospital
Section 1. The name of Sibalom Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Sibalom, Province of Antique, is hereby changed to Delegate Ramon Maza, Sr. Memorial Hospital.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 13, 1980
